OL,6,FEight men have been convicted of sex
OL,7,Foffences after grooming underage girls.
OL,9,FThe men, who preyed on schoolgirls
OL,10,Faged between 13 and 15 in the Blackrod
OL,11,Farea of Bolton between 2016 and 2018,
OL,12,Fwere found guilty of offences
OL,13,Fincluding rape and sexual assault on
OL,14,FTuesday following a trial at Liverpool
OL,15,FCrown Court, a spokesman for Greater
OL,16,FManchester Police said.
