OL,3,CEight men convicted of sex offences
OL,4,Cafter grooming girls
OL,6,FThey would get to know victims at a
OL,7,Fcommunity centre and message them on
OL,8,Fsocial media, initiating sexual
OL,9,Fconversations, as well as plying them
OL,10,Fwith alcohol and drugs, police said.
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Samantha Parry
OL,13,Fsaid: "Thank you to all the brave
OL,14,Fyoung women who took the difficult
OL,15,Fstep to come forward and report this
OL,16,Fabuse to the police.
OL,18,F"Thanks to your courage, you have
OL,19,Fhelped remove a group of dangerous
OL,20,Fdepraved sexual offenders from the
OL,21,Fstreets of Blackrod and Bolton.
