OL,3,CEight men convicted of sex offences
OL,4,Cafter grooming girls
OL,6,F"I hope today's verdicts bring a sense
OL,7,Fof justice for the victims-survivors
OL,8,Fand reassurance for the community.
OL,10,F"I'd like to take this chance to reach
OL,11,Fout to all victim-survivors of sexual
OL,12,Fabuse and let them know that we are
OL,13,Fhere to listen to you when you are
OL,14,Fready and will work at a pace that is
OL,15,Fcomfortable for you.
OL,17,F"We take sexual offences very
OL,18,Fseriously, no matter the passage of
OL,19,Ftime since it took place."
