OL,3,CEight men convicted of sex offences
OL,4,Cafter grooming girls
OL,6,FThe force said some of the offences
OL,7,Ftook place at the home of Cory
OL,8,FBarrett, 24, who was found guilty of
OL,9,Fthree counts of rape, one count of
OL,10,Foral rape and one count of sexual
OL,11,Fassault by penetration.
OL,13,FBarrett, of Wigan, would invite
OL,14,Ffriends to the rented property in
OL,15,FBlackrod where they would use drugs
OL,16,Fand drink alcohol.
OL,18,FJack Poulson, 31, and Daniel Flatters,
OL,19,F34, both of Bolton, stayed over at the
OL,20,Fhouse on a regular basis.
