OL,3,CEight men convicted of sex offences
OL,4,Cafter grooming girls
OL,6,FPoulson was convicted of two counts of
OL,7,Frape, five counts of sexual activity
OL,8,Fwith a child under 16, one count of
OL,9,Fcausing a person to engage in sexual
OL,10,Factivity without consent, one count of
OL,11,Finciting a child to engage in sexual
OL,12,Factivity, and one count of sexual
OL,13,Fcommunications with a child.
OL,15,FFlatters was found guilty of four
OL,16,Fcounts of sexual activity with a child
OL,17,Funder the age of 16.
OL,19,FAhead of the trial, he pleaded guilty
OL,20,Fto supplying cocaine and aggravated
OL,21,Ftaking without consent, police said.
