OL,6,FThe group's offending came to light
OL,7,Fwhen one of their victims, a 15-year-
OL,8,Fold girl, was injured in a car crash
OL,9,Fwith Flatters and her friends became
OL,10,Fsuspicious.
OL,12,FThe other men convicted were James
OL,13,FFitzgerald, 36, of Bolton, who was
OL,14,Ffound guilty of one count of sexual
OL,15,Fassault by penetration.
