OL,6,FRichard Haslam 35, of Bolton, was
OL,7,Ffound guilty of two counts of rape,
OL,8,Fone count of oral rape, two counts of
OL,9,Fsexual activity with a child under 16
OL,10,Fand one count of causing a child to
OL,11,Fengage in sexual activity.
OL,13,FBrandon Harwood, 25, of Bolton, was
OL,14,Ffound guilty of one count of rape, one
OL,15,Fcount of attempted oral rape and one
OL,16,Fcount of sexual activity with a child
OL,17,Funder 16.
OL,19,FHarvie Aspden, 25, of Bolton, was
OL,20,Ffound guilty of two counts of sexual
OL,21,Factivity with a child under 16.
